{"tid":17092,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【第一次世界大戰的遠因｜認識歷史】","createTime":"2016-12-01T16:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T02:46:12.000Z","uid":36952,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b739e9f93f24e290dd7a6ccd59a857ea06a26658","tid":17092,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"第一次世界大戰，係人類歷史上一場極為重要既戰爭，背景發生係1914年至1918年，係人類史上第一場全球性規模既大型戰爭，由於主要戰場係歐洲，所以又稱為歐戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/8/7489/15440346944_f24f3fbb20_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F8%2F7489%2F15440346944_f24f3fbb20_b.jpg&h=d71bab9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時戰爭國主要可以分成兩邊，分別係同盟國（德﹑奧匈﹑土耳其）同協約國（英﹑法﹑俄﹑意）。<br />\n開戰既原因主要歸類為極端民族主義﹑同盟對立﹑軍備競賽﹑同埋殖民地爭奪等等，加上戰前危機既出現，引起大戰發生。<br />\n<br />\n1.\t極端民族主義<br />\n自從德國係1870年既普法戰爭統一之後，法國一直對戰爭既條款十分不滿，例如德(普王)威廉一世係位於法國既凡爾賽宮入面既鏡廳宣告建立德意志帝國，法國人民對於呢樣野一直係耿耿於懷，埋下左兩國於日後對立既伏線，法國國內復仇主義盛行。<br />\n<br />\n宣告建立德意志帝國<br />\n<img src=\"http://l7.alamy.com/zooms/cfa5bc2bf3544560ba70a47d619028fc/events-franco-prussian-war-1870-1871-proclamation-of-the-germen-emperor-ba1gtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fl7.alamy.com%2Fzooms%2Fcfa5bc2bf3544560ba70a47d619028fc%2Fevents-franco-prussian-war-1870-1871-proclamation-of-the-germen-emperor-ba1gtp.jpg&h=6fc3fdc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國學校教導有關因為普法戰爭而失去阿爾薩斯-洛林既情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/00/1887_Bettanier_Der_Schwarze_Fleck_anagoria.JPG \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F00%2F1887_Bettanier_Der_Schwarze_Fleck_anagoria.JPG%20&h=9e7113d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.\t同盟對立<br />\n普法戰爭後，德國總理俾斯麥擔心法國報復，所以希望透過結盟政策孤立法國，引起左一條又一條既同盟條約出現，例如三帝同盟﹑三國同盟﹑德奧同盟等等，最後可以歸類為兩邊，分別係義大利、德國和奧匈既三國同盟(1882)，以及法國、英國和俄國既三國協約(1907)。同盟內容主要圍繞住當自己國被打，其他同盟國要互相協助，引致戰爭時候引起連鎖效應。<br />\n三國同盟<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4044/4639736972_261f059a05_o.png \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4044%2F4639736972_261f059a05_o.png%20&h=4f2511ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三國協約<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0c/Triple_Entente.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F0c%2FTriple_Entente.jpg&h=0de19e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國漫畫描述因為塞爾維亞被奧匈攻擊，以致俄國攻擊奧匈，引起德國攻擊俄國，再因而被英法攻擊的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Bs2D0FnCMAA1kIW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBs2D0FnCMAA1kIW.jpg&h=783ea4fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b45de4b721f7676263108ef9460e89ad901a8476","tid":17092,"uid":48482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"留明睇大戰"},{"pid":"e0ec740e1b853b5bd8cad81f91597edac45324ed","tid":17092,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"樓主小學畢業未<br />\n中學咪讀過晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148065281a1004448507ee6067ac7992a9445da9","tid":17092,"uid":34876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主小學畢業未<br />\n中學咪讀過晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高中冇揀歷史咪唔識囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得你一個睇post?出番去啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:以前讀歷史"},{"pid":"e6b1af8726f8faa8a61d6c507711572664ef6266","tid":17092,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"讀history 讀過<br />\n不過二戰感覺多野睇同影響大d(對近代)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aeccf603abefb123472ab78c04ce3bd1616ea17","tid":17092,"uid":27066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:25:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6f339cff4bf31