D&h=10a81b29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://c1.staticflickr.com/8/7489/15440346944_f24f3fbb20_b.jpg[/img][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n當時戰爭國主要可以分成兩邊，分別係同盟國（德﹑奧匈﹑土耳其）同協約國（英﹑法﹑俄﹑意）。<br />\n開戰既原因主要歸類為極端民族主義﹑同盟對立﹑軍備競賽﹑同埋殖民地爭奪等等，加上戰前危機既出現，引起大戰發生。<br />\n<br />\n1.\t極端民族主義<br />\n自從德國係1870年既普法戰爭統一之後，法國一直對戰爭既條款十分不滿，例如德(普王)威廉一世係位於法國既凡爾賽宮入面既鏡廳宣告建立德意志帝國，法國人民對於呢樣野一直係耿耿於懷，埋下左兩國於日後對立既伏線，法國國內復仇主義盛行。<br />\n<br />\n宣告建立德意志帝國<br />\n[img] [url]<a href=\"http://l7.alamy.com/zooms/cfa5bc2bf3544560ba70a47d619028fc/events-franco-prussian-war-1870-1871-proclamation-of-the-germen-emperor-ba1gtp.jpg[/img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fl7.alamy.com%2Fzooms%2Fcfa5bc2bf3544560ba70a47d619028fc%2Fevents-franco-prussian-war-1870-1871-proclamation-of-the-germen-emperor-ba1gtp.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c7a08148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://l7.alamy.com/zooms/cfa5bc2bf3544560ba70a47d619028fc/events-franco-prussian-war-1870-1871-proclamation-of-the-germen-emperor-ba1gtp.jpg[/img][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n法國學校教導有關因為普法戰爭而失去阿爾薩斯-洛林既情況<br />\n[img]  <a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/00/1887_Bettanier_Der_Schwarze_Fleck_anagoria.JPG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F00%2F1887_Bettanier_Der_Schwarze_Fleck_anagoria.JPG&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=080f86ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/00/1887_Bettanier_Der_Schwarze_Fleck_anagoria.JPG</a> [/img]<br />\n<br />\n2.\t同盟對立<br />\n普法戰爭後，德國總理俾斯麥擔心法國報復，所以希望透過結盟政策孤立法國，引起左一條又一條既同盟條約出現，例如三帝同盟﹑三國同盟﹑德奧同盟等等，最後可以歸類為兩邊，分別係義大利、德國和奧匈既三國同盟(1882)，以及法國、英國和俄國既三國協約(1907)。同盟內容主要圍繞住當自己國被打，其他同盟國要互相協助，引致戰爭時候引起連鎖效應。<br />\n三國同盟<br />\n[img]  <a href=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4044/4639736972_261f059a05_o.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4044%2F4639736972_261f059a05_o.png&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7b9fcc95\" target=\"_blank\">https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4044/4639736972_261f059a05_o.png</a> [/img]<br />\n<br />\n三國協約<br />\n[img] [url]<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0c/Triple_Entente.jpg[/img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F0c%2FTriple_Entente.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=60ec8fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0c/Triple_Entente.jpg[/img][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n美國漫畫描述因為塞爾維亞被奧匈攻擊，以致俄國攻擊奧匈，引起德國攻擊俄國，再因而被英法攻擊的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Bs2D0FnCMAA1kIW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBs2D0FnCMAA1kIW.jpg&h=783ea4fa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1001 了"},{"pid":"05ec1789e20bd21ff94b7fd0801715eb6d25d9c8","tid":17092,"uid":47426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-14T23:42:57.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"d7b987d5f27285f25bfbbf8a8b0392f988f74f7b","tid":17092,"uid":8353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:41:03.000Z","msg":"可唔可以介紹下冷戰啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ce685ae8da46f666eac54eef3b837e833ffefb","tid":17092,"uid":66695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:43:42.000Z","msg":"Google都有啦<br />\n洗撚睇你咩"},{"pid":"e72048f9c594ee1d4ce45f0a26679719916d0fd0","tid":17092,"uid":34969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0f0dec847410fc884b3344848e799ee2fbcd478f","tid":17092,"uid":60355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"加油巴打，支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5458394c00a5c5066f71f1f558cebc7011e8d5c","tid":17092,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油巴打，支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一戰係度講曬啦巴打，多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/17107/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/17107/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b67b8f11d803a7723ba368157d8647fa5f816e45","tid":17092,"uid":68192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"原來係同一位巴打 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}